            "title": " A Manifesto from the community of Kokvitskaya Gora.",
            "summary": "2020 / Community projekts / Art book A proposed public statement calling&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 6\">\n<div class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 6\">\n<div class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><em>2020 / Community projekts / Art book</em></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>A proposed public statement calling for a better <span style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\">quality of life for the people from this community.</span></p>\n<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 6\">\n<div class=\"section\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>The manifesto proposal emerged from my research \"Kokvitskaya Gora - the process of standing for community rights\". The work focuses on the Komi community of Kokvitskaya Gora.</p>\n<p>After the field research of the place, I decided to offer the residents a manifesto to make a public statement demanding improvements in the quality of life for the people of Kokvitskaya Gora. By choosing this artistic form, I hope to perceive the text not as the physical result of my scientific activity, but as a process.</p>\n<p>The book is a collaborative work of local residents and artists.</p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-14.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-14-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-14-1.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-14-1-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-14-3.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-14-3-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-15.jpg\" data-size=\"4032x3024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://nikagrigorian.com/media/posts/2/gallery/image-20-07-21-10-15-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
